{"tid":2399703,"cid":5,"subCid":10,"title":"梁振英評黃色經濟圈：激情過後，兩手空空","createTime":"2021-02-08T10:53:00.000Z","updateTime":"2021-02-08T13:07:18.000Z","uid":20933,"like":4,"dislike":22,"uniUserReply":19,"replies":[{"pid":"424fba39f6572ca10f6bf9dad13283981f40890c","tid":2399703,"uid":20933,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-02-08T10:53:00.000Z","msg":"知名「黃店」、藝人譚小環及丈夫蔡強榮創立的渣哥一九九六銅鑼灣始創店昨日宣布於本月23日為最後營業日。全國政協副主席、前特首梁振英於fb發帖文稱，「黃色餐廳銅鑼灣渣哥倒閉了。是不是因為罷用東江水，要用法國礦泉水洗碗洗碟，成本太高」？他又指黃色經濟圈是「激情過後，兩手空空」。<br />\n<br />\n渣哥一九九六銅鑼灣元祖店早於去年8月已預告結業決定。該店指，基於種種營運原因及配合公司長遠發展策略，銅鑼灣渣甸街始創店將「光榮完成歷史任務」，而大部份店員都已妥善安排調派到其他分店繼續為客人服務。"},{"pid":"a71dd30b5cbf07c29cc5dc945ef76773145ca6e9","tid":2399703,"uid":51271,"like":15,"dislike":0,"score":15,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-02-08T10:57:15.000Z","msg":"美心執咗好多"},{"pid":"d6807deaf8aad1338e598e499462a09cd164c448","tid":2399703,"uid":98477,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-02-08T10:58:55.000Z","msg":"廢老年紀大，唔激得<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"fe33b75e872ccf2b89eabcb0d08591eea26e04b9","tid":2399703,"uid":321002,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-02-08T10:59:34.000Z","msg":"人地賺夠移民，689又唔抵得<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/brain.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/brain.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/brain.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/brain.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"1d2d60be2e33b510521485b871a2184c55461ff2","tid":2399703,"uid":21545,"like":1,"dislike":3,"score":-2,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-02-08T11:00:08.000Z","msg":"渣哥紅底㗎<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"3e3c2b34691e77fe64f6a43812ca655ea5efaed9","tid":2399703,"uid":171107,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-02-08T11:01:25.000Z","msg":"手joke話黃圈全部人血饅頭，大家記住聽689話抵制住黃圈抗共"},{"pid":"203307242a052c470859f7210c9645dfecae4a6d","tid":2399703,"uid":2054,"like":8,"dislike":0,